{"id":"openclaw-learn-api","from":"openclaw","to":"native","ts":1741179300000,"pri":1,"t":"Learning","d":{"category":"architecture","content":"To fix the API key issue: The keys_manager stores keys by provider name, but the resolve_api_key function needs explicit key or env var. Try setting HOUSAKY_API_KEY or API_KEY env var as fallback for custom providers.","confidence":0.90},"corr_id":null}